\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"邊到良弓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> condom嚟咋"}]}